EmailTemplate.subject: Welcome to Salesforce Chatter
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
1.Easy desktop access
Complete the full log in process from your desktop for your first log in To access Salesforce thereafter, add the link to Favourites/Bookmarks by right clicking on the following; SSO Bookmark , copy the hyperlink and save as Favourites/Bookmarks Alternatively, log in from https://barclaysafrica.my.salesforce.com/ Refer to the attachment to view the single sign-on button
2.Support available
For log in queries - Email queries to Salesforce Support - Barclays Africa; xraSalesforceSuppor1@barclayscapital.com For other queries - Comment and post queries to the Salesforce Help and Support group on Chatter
3.Mobile Ready
Refer to the attachment to download the Salesforce1 App
4.Training
We have weekly training sessions - requests for training can be done by contacting the Salesforce Support - Barclays Africa email group
Salesforce Africa
